result.name: Mini Cooker

reviews.text: Good value for the price
Good. Honest waitress. Delicious food.

This hidden restaurant was completely unnoticeable to me. Compared to the restaurant’s size, the menu in Mini Cooker was quite ambitiously big. Food was actually quite good, but the serving speed was limited by the size of its tiny kitchen.
Tiny place (6 tables), with very nice all day breakfast. I liked a lot the set with the buttery croissants.
Great food. Love this little cafe.

result.name: 小灶子

reviews.text: 試過哂所有食品都好好味， 不時也會更新餐牌，推介！👍👍👍👍👍

舖仔細細，只得十二個座位，但食物非常得……
軟殼蟹香草忌廉意粉， 墨西哥烤雞卷， 士多啤梨窩夫城堡。
多款式，價錢公道, 門囗不起眼同五坐得多人

小商場小鋪子，鋪面約六張桌，有時候需要等候。
午市叫了墨汁帶子意粉。
整體不錯，咖啡一般般。
溫馨小店，即製食物，誠意可嘉；）
